# Hawke's Bay County, Hastings Borough, and Havelock North Town Board Empowering Act 1929Local Act1929 No 13

Date of assent1 November 1929

## Contents

[Title][0]
    
*   [Preamble][1]

[1][2] [Short Title][2]

[2][3] [Authority to make contributions][3]

